Posts.Content: Dr. Partin did my open surgery two years ago with great results. Johns Hopkins fanatisk when I asked Dr. Partin why I should choose Hopkins over my local hospital his response was they may do more in a week than my local hospital does in a year. I am not sure if that is true but it made sense it me. You will not regret going to Johns Hopkins.

Posts.Content: Dr. Partin did mine Dec. 2013 I couldn't have been more pleased with my results and my treatment at Johns Hopkins. I had open surgery no problems at all.
